command of the mongodb 

* To CREATE database : use database_name

* To DELETE database -> select database : use existing_database_name -> db.dropDatabase() 

* To to USE / goTo database : use existing_database_name

* To CREATE object/document/COLLECTION -> first select the database : use database_name -> and then : db.createCollection('collection_name')


* To DELETE COLLECTION -> use existing_database_name -> db.collection_name.deleteOne({key_name: "valueEqualTo"})

